{"tid":2127812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"病床就快爆滿，武漢肺炎患者周街走既日子已經不遠","createTime":"2020-07-27T13:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T14:03:57.000Z","uid":73915,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"53b4d96775153ecec1597a57195670b384fd851d","tid":2127812,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"仲有30張病床，想有床就快d感染霸左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJACXxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJACXxb.png&h=d2847cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局總行政經理（病人安全及風險管理）何婉霞表示，2019冠狀病毒病確診個案增加，對公立醫院隔離病床供應構成很大壓力，醫管局會採取多項措施增加供應，並加快病床流轉。<br />\n <br />\n何婉霞今日在簡報會上表示，扣除需維修的病床數目，公立醫院目前約有1,150多張隔離病床。醫管局會在可行情況下，暫緩年度維修保養計劃，以保留足夠一線隔離病床接收有需要的病人。<br />\n <br />\n醫管局已陸續啟動二線隔離病床，希望增加病房接收病人的能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/07/20200712/20200712_183005_030.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F07%2F20200712%2F20200712_183005_030.html&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=72350059\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/07/20200712/20200712_183005_030.html</a>"},{"pid":"90591ccfe0fa64705e9486b5ce9c6fd962d80f6d","tid":2127812,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b4d96775153ecec1597a57195670b384fd851d","tid":2127812,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:49:25.000Z","msg":"仲有30張病床，想有床就快d感染霸左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJACXxb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJACXxb.png&h=d2847cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局總行政經理（病人安全及風險管理）何婉霞表示，2019冠狀病毒病確診個案增加，對公立醫院隔離病床供應構成很大壓力，醫管局會採取多項措施增加供應，並加快病床流轉。<br />\n <br />\n何婉霞今日在簡報會上表示，扣除需維修的病床數目，公立醫院目前約有1,150多張隔離病床。醫管局會在可行情況下，暫緩年度維修保養計劃，以保留足夠一線隔離病床接收有需要的病人。<br />\n <br />\n醫管局已陸續啟動二線隔離病床，希望增加病房接收病人的能力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/07/20200712/20200712_183005_030.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F07%2F20200712%2F20200712_183005_030.html&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpa7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=72350059\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/07/20200712/20200712_183005_030.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"高觀屋奇一日油"},{"pid":"38ec557a00131bea87cdc76599500d2fb8155330","tid":2127812,"uid":284595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:52:15.000Z","msg":"最後手段係不再提供治療"},{"pid":"e8dc3f84cf6a4303bbcc8ed30354dadee183c8e0","tid":2127812,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38ec557a00131bea87cdc76599500d2fb8155330","tid":2127812,"uid":284595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:52:15.000Z","msg":"最後手段係不再提供治療"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"冇啦，今日感染已經冇床"},{"pid":"154d303f83e8a0490dd5703dff8e5bd99fe15022","tid":2127812,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"輕症去2線床，再唔係去晒亞博隔離"},{"pid":"0d126251fbd0aace41ca0e63b48d8d03f097fb83","tid":2127812,"uid":125727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"每日有幾十人出院wo<br />\n出院準則假陰性都照放<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9ee9d12e8a08b1ad760d46d45c7300784a43c9","tid":2127812,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T13:59:46.000Z","msg":"大把人一早感染左等兩三日都未入到醫院呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95de505d0c1289f3515b4313270849ed5340122","tid":2127812,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T14:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" clas